The first patch doesn't apply to 2.5.45. cmd_len was removed in 2.5.45.
This one should be ok, right?
--- ide-cd.c.orig	Sun Nov  3 16:34:38 2002
+++ ide-cd.c	Sun Nov  3 16:36:52 2002
@@ -884,6 +884,7 @@
